product.title: ARB/OME Lift Kit - 2" Light Load w/ Shackle and Pins FJ60, FJ62 1985-1990
product.body_html:
Fits Toyota Land Cruiser 4/1985-1/1990 FJ60/FJ62

Kit includes the following: 

2 x 593-111 - Front - 2" Lifted Leaf Spring - Stock/Light Load - CS003F
2 x 593-112 - Nitrocharger Sport Shock - Front - Light Load - 60009 
2 x 593-115 - 2" Lifted Leaf Spring, Rear - Stock/Light Load - CS017RB
2 x 593-116 - Nitrocharger Sport Shock, Rear - Light Load - 60062 
4 x 593-122 - Leaf Spring Bushing Kit - OMESB1 
4 x 593-123 - U-Bolts - OMEU51 
4 x 593-124 - U-Bolts - OMEU59B 
1 x 593-127 - Old man Emu - Steering Stabilizer - OMESD24 
1 x 593-128 - Greaseable Front Shackle - OMEGS2 
1 x 593-129 - Greaseable Rear Shackle - OMEGS1 
2 x 593-130 - Greaseable Pin - OMEGP1
